	section#about.about
		.about__wrapper
			.about__img
				img(src="/img/maria-fpo.jpg")
			.about__info
				h1.about__head About Me
				p.about__copy I'm a visual and UX designer with over 15 years of experience designing for businesses and nonprofits; and over 8 years designing and managing web design projects. Along with UX and visual design, my experience includes concept development and interactive project management. I hold a BFA in Graphic Design from Texas Christian University, and an MFA in Design from the School of Visual Arts. I live in lovely Ditmas Park, Brooklyn with my husband and son.
				p.about__copy I’m currently taking on offsite UX, visual design, print, branding & illustration projects. I'm unable to consider onsite opportunities at the moment. Recruiters: please do not contact.
				a.link(href='mailto:me@mariadelaguardia.com') me@mariadelaguardia.com
			.about__list
				h2.about__list-head Capabilities
				ul
					li.about__list-item Information architecture & user experience
					li.about__list-item UI & visual design
					li.about__list-item Visual brand identity
					li.about__list-item Print design
					li.about__list-item Illustration
					li.about__list-item Web development  #[small.about__list-item--small in collaboration with my development partners]
					li.about__list-item Interactive project management
			.about__img.about__img--second
				img.project__image--single(src="/img/maria-fpo.jpg")

